{"tid":2263780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得搭𨋢都要考牌","createTime":"2020-10-30T06:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T06:59:03.000Z","uid":356471,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d1af6cf66114486bcf5f6092983f3e855291ba3","tid":2263780,"uid":356471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:47:28.000Z","msg":"1. 第一個入𨋢，撳完自已去幾多樓之後就企左喺啲掣前面... 咁我點撳😞<br />\n<br />\n2.企係啲掣前面，但係唔幫手撳閂門掣⋯要慢慢等部𨋢自已閂😞<br />\n<br />\n3.依家肺炎你怕污糟唔想撳，咁或者企後少少都好😞<br />\n<br />\n3. 人地入面差唔多閂晒門，你先係出面撳𨋢。ok可能你趕時間，但係入黎之後冇表示⋯示意下自己唔好意思都好丫😞 <br />\n<br />\n4. 比你入到黎啦，我去G樓，你入黎就同我撳1樓😞本來可以直落地下，但係就要停一停一樓比你出😞<br />\n<br />\n5.仲有冇人有補充😞"},{"pid":"dabddfe75655ae26698f12000ff3790cb125aab1","tid":2263780,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:49:06.000Z","msg":"係咪女人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a127a45dc4469acb543f65c24d559851a553a0c","tid":2263780,"uid":345520,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"人哋住一樓返屋企都唔俾人㩒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aef0f378673b27343eb22ff5473faa8a781e725","tid":2263780,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"最鍾意補住臨閂晒門嗰下先㩒開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nl"},{"pid":"5fc3cbed9e60c8d1279f0b69858ea339e2eceffa","tid":2263780,"uid":118830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"落樓入𨋢老奉唔撳閂門"}]}